DASPublisher is a tool for generating digital presentations of academic design
work from a simple file system archive. 

* Output formats supported include mobile phone, tablet, and desktop interactive applications; 
* QR Code tagging for all digital artifacts
* Interactive or automatic slideshow

Archive Format
--------------

File Formats
------------

Supported file formats are as follows:

* JPG, GIF, PNG, TIF
* PDF (single and multi-page)

